{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der aktuellen Gesundheitspolitik herrscht der Widersinn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.920", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Beamtinnen und Beamte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ja per Definition dem Gemeinwohl dienen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch eine faktische Pflicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich privat zu versichern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.240", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gezwungen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.920", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau dieses Gemeinwohl mit F\u00fc\u00dfen zu treten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Beamtinnen und Beamten sind die dickste Rosine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich die privaten Krankenversicherungen herausgepickt haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.360", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne Beamtinnen und Beamten w\u00e4ren die privaten Krankenversicherungen \u00fcberhaupt nicht lebensf\u00e4hig; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn \u00fcber die H\u00e4lfte der knapp 9\u00a0Millionen Privatversicherten sind Beamtinnen und Beamte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die private Versicherungsindustrie ohne staatliche Beihilfezahlungen als Vollversicherung \u00fcberhaupt nicht existent w\u00e4re."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dieser teuren Subventionierung der Versicherungsindustrie auf Kosten der Allgemeinheit muss Schluss sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.440", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Art der Versicherung f\u00fcr Staatsdienerinnen und Staatsdiener ist nicht im Interesse des Staates, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.920", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sie ist einzig und allein im Interesse der Lobby der Privatversicherungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.040", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu der bekannterma\u00dfen auch unser Gesundheitsminister Spahn geh\u00f6rt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beamtinnen und Beamte haben zwar auf dem Papier die Wahlm\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich entweder privat oder freiwillig gesetzlich zu versichern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tats\u00e4chlich allerdings haben sie diese Wahl nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn sie sich privat versichern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.960", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bekommen sie \u00fcber Beihilfen 50 bis 80\u00a0Prozent der Kosten f\u00fcr medizinische Leistungen erstattet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn sie sich dagegen freiwillig gesetzlich versichern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen sie neben dem Arbeitnehmeranteil sogar noch den Arbeitgeberanteil \u00fcbernehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der finanzielle Nachteil ist so gro\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.880", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie faktisch gar keine andere M\u00f6glichkeit haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als sich privat zu versichern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit unserem Antrag wollen wir einerseits den Beamtinnen und Beamten eine echte Wahlm\u00f6glichkeit geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00f6chten aber andererseits die Zweiklassenmedizin aufbrechen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch Besserverdiener sollen mit ihren hohen Beitr\u00e4gen in die Solidargemeinschaft der gesetzlichen Krankenversicherung einbezogen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke fordert deshalb gemeinsam mit Gewerkschaften und Sozialverb\u00e4nden die Einf\u00fchrung einer solidarisch finanzierten Gesundheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Pflegeversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.520", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in die alle nach ihren M\u00f6glichkeiten einzahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aus allen Einkommensarten und ohne Beitragsbemessungsgrenze."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.160", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der SPD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.800", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben im Wahlkampf eine B\u00fcrgerversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.080", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn auch nur eine B\u00fcrgerversicherung light, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gefordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Einbeziehung der Beamtinnen und Beamten in die gesetzliche Krankenversicherung ist ein wichtiger Schritt dahin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.360", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben heute die M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.440", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einmal f\u00fcr eine Forderung zu stimmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie im Wahlkampf erhoben haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.400", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Ihre Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeit w\u00e4re das nicht schlecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.040", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die privaten Krankenversicherungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.200", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben viele Nachteile, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.240", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sie in ihren Imagebrosch\u00fcren nicht erw\u00e4hnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So ist es zum Beispiel so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.760", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass gerade im Alter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn das Einkommen sinkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Beitr\u00e4ge enorm ansteigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.160", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es mit einem enormen Kostenrisiko verbunden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.720", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Privatversicherte oder ihre Kinder Vorerkrankungen haben oder chronisch krank werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.680", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen zun\u00e4chst den Beamtinnen und Beamten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.400", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann aber auch allen anderen den Weg aus der Kostenfalle \u201eprivate Krankenversicherung\u201c erm\u00f6glichen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.000", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die echte Wahlm\u00f6glichkeit f\u00fcr Beamtinnen und Beamte ist ein wichtiger Schritt hin zur solidarischen Gesundheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Pflegeversicherung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch die Einbeziehung aller Einkommensarten und durch die Abschaffung der Zusatzbeitr\u00e4ge und der Beitragsbemessungsgrenze kann die Zweiklassenmedizin \u00fcberwunden werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So k\u00f6nnen wir das Gesundheitssystem dauerhaft und solide finanzieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir k\u00f6nnen allen die bestm\u00f6gliche Gesundheitsversorgung garantieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.840", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns diesen ersten Schritt heute gemeinsam machen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.000", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bedanke mich f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ebenfalls zu Ihrer ersten Rede rufe ich die Kollegin Petra Nicolaisen von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion auf."
   ]
  }
 ]
}